subject: Re: [EVP-ITC] Still nothin"!
author: Zack Widup
full_text:
There have been no indications of upcoming earthquakes on the ULF-ELF 
group I'm on, either. Maybe these guys can't really predict the future so 
well. I don't think they always lie.
:-)

Zack

On Mon, 12 Nov 2007, Frank Sumption wrote:

>
> Still no EQ in China, lying swine voices! I don't get that , I can get 
> stuff that's clearly not broadcast fragments, or anything else Earthly, 
> why the lying crap, and why the false prophecy? Who was it that was 
> quoting someone that said the spirits always lie?
>
> I think ya have to ask the questions about what it is, I think you have 
> to go out on that limb and see what's out there, even if it doesn't fit 
> anyone's paradigm. I think those that think they have the knowledge to 
> ask the right questions, and can discern who's who in the unseen 
> world.....are fools. I have these crack heads insist I'm their girl, 
> their Little Purple Space Princess, yes it resonates, or whatever you'd 
> call it, but I wouldn't trade my soul for it. The word "contract" has 
> come up many times in my recordings, and I always tell them there ain't 
> no damn contract! I go to nothingness first. Religious or not, there 's 
> somthing out there that buys/collects souls, and it is not a metaphor! 
> You must choose your steps in life wisely, but fearlessly. Never, ever 
> say "I'll do anything for....".
>
>   Frank-S
>
